      "content": "---\ntitle: 用户留存\nupdated: 2017-02-28 06:29:19Z\ncreated: 2017-02-28 06:23:27Z\nsource: http://www.gamelook.com.cn/2016/03/245274\nauthor: tangyongfeng@gmail.com\n---\n\n\n\n\n<en-note><div>提高用户留存的基本功能：</div><div>1、社交功能</div><div>2、竞争系统</div><div>3、成就感</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>用户流失的原因：</div><div><br/></div><div><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">1、重大的挫败感，比如出了新手保护后被熟练玩家狂虐，大量库存物资或建筑被摧毁。</span><br STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">2、较高的难度障碍，在某个关卡或某个任务Boss前多次尝试失败，其实也是挫败感的一种。</span><br STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">3、失去目标，达成阶段目标后突然失去下一步的目标，或者下一步目标过于遥远短期失去动力。个别的也存在无法理解游戏的引导，不知道下一步的目标该如何实现。</span><br STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">4、缺乏成就，缺乏让自己能产生愉悦的目标达成和头衔，荣誉。</span><br STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">5、疲劳，反复从事重复性的任务，消耗时间和精力但失去了游戏的乐趣。</span><br STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">6、遭到侮辱，在游戏中遭到人身攻击，谩骂，以及其他玩家羞辱。</span><br STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">7、跟随，游戏中的好友或者队友撤出，跟随撤出游戏。</span></div><div><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">8、吃亏，在游戏中和其他玩家对抗显著吃亏，无法达到平衡。一些活动设计不合理，或者营销设计不合理，也会造成玩家的吃亏感。</span></div><div><span STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span STYLE=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br/></span></span></span></div><div><span STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span STYLE=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span STYLE=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br/></span></span></span></div></en-note>      ",
